.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people prefer 5 different music-genres: reggae, rock, hip-hop, soul, d&b
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: western, thriller, musical, mystery, comedy
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: reggaemaster, september, july, april, october
5 different pets are kept: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. the person watching western movies is the fan of hip-hop
2. the person watching swedish movies is the owner of the dog
3. the person watching thriller movies is the person drinking tea
4. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of soul
5. the fan of rock is the person drinking coffee
6. the person who's birthday is in july is the owner of the bird
7. the fan of d&b is the person who's birthday is in september
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the owner of the cat
11. the owner of the horses is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september
12. the person who's birthday is in reggaemaster is the person drinking beer
13. the person watching musical movies is the person who's birthday is in april
14. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the fan of reggae
15. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
